From: Mathieu Poirier <mathieu.poirier@linaro.org>
Date: Fri, 7 Apr 2023 10:14:29 -0600
Subject: [PATCH] remoteproc: imx_dsp_rproc: Fix kernel test robot sparse
 warning
References: bsc#1012628
